normalization: min-max normalization of raw_mu within TEST period

metadata.ground_truth_description: raw_mu = average daily return over next 21 days
metadata.rho_description: rho = (raw_mu - min_raw_mu) / (max_raw_mu - min_raw_mu) [computed within TEST period]
metadata.trend_label_description: trend_label = 1.0 if raw_mu > 0 else 0.0 (for MSU Stage 1 binary classification)
